==English==
===Adjective===
'''westerly'''
#situated in the [[west]]
#(''of wind'') coming from the west
===Adverb===
'''westerly'''
#towards the west
#sometimes used by Land Surveyors when "West" is what they intend to say but are afraid to make a commitment

===Noun===
'''westerly'''  (''plural'' westerlies)
#a westerly wind or [[storm]]
